---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'What is OpenClaw?',
    a: 'OpenClaw is an open-source AI gateway that runs on your machine. It connects AI language models (like Claude, GPT, Gemini) to messaging channels (Telegram, Discord), tools, APIs, and automation systems. Think of it as the operating system for your personal AI workforce.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What skill level do I need?',
    a: 'The Personal Edition assumes zero programming experience — just basic computer skills and the ability to follow step-by-step instructions. The Business Edition introduces more advanced concepts but remains accessible. The Enterprise Edition is for people ready to build serious automation systems and includes pre-built scripts so you can learn by deploying.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Does this work on Mac, Windows, and Linux?',
    a: 'Yes. OpenClaw runs anywhere Node.js runs — Windows, macOS, and Linux. The Enterprise Edition includes install scripts for both PowerShell (Windows) and Bash (macOS/Linux). Every instruction in the guide includes platform-specific notes where needed.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How is this different from YouTube tutorials or free guides?',
    a: 'Free tutorials cover individual pieces — one video on Telegram bots, another on AI APIs, another on cron jobs. The Blueprint is a complete, tested system where every component is designed to work together. No gaps, no outdated steps, no "left as an exercise for the reader." You build a production system from chapter 1 to chapter 24.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I need coding experience?',
    a: 'For Personal Edition, no. You\'ll copy configuration files and follow instructions. For Business and Enterprise, basic comfort with the command line helps, but the guide teaches everything you need. You\'ll learn by building — every concept is paired with an implementation you actually deploy.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What\'s the refund policy?',
    a: 'Full 30-day money-back guarantee, no questions asked. If the Blueprint doesn\'t deliver the value you expected, email us and we\'ll refund you immediately. We\'d rather have happy builders than reluctant customers.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I get updates when new content is added?',
    a: 'Yes. All editions include free updates as the guide evolves. When OpenClaw releases new features or we add new chapters, you\'ll get the updated PDF automatically. Business Edition includes 12 months of priority updates. Enterprise includes lifetime updates.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How much does it cost to run the AI system after setup?',
    a: 'Infrastructure is free — OpenClaw is open source and runs on your machine. The main ongoing cost is AI model usage, which typically runs $1-5/day for personal use and $5-15/day for heavy business use. The guide teaches smart engine routing that can reduce costs by 60-80% compared to using premium models for everything.',
  },
];
---

<section class="section-spacing section-padding relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 reveal">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="color: var(--color-accent-cyan);">
        FAQ
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-4">
        Common
        <span class="gradient-text">Questions</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      {faqs.map((faq, i) => (
        <div class="faq-item reveal" style={`transition-delay: ${i * 0.04}s;`}>
          <details class="glass-card rounded-xl overflow-hidden group">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-white/[0.02]">
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold pr-4 transition-colors duration-300 group-open:text-[var(--color-accent-blue)]">{faq.q}</h3>
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-white/[0.04]"
                style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                <svg class="faq-chevron w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <div class="px-6 pb-6">
                <div class="h-px w-full mb-5" style="background: var(--color-border);"></div>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                  {faq.a}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
